    <item>
      <title>南非再次选举西里尔·拉马福萨为总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-18/south-africa-reelects-cyril-ramaphosa-as-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在西里尔·拉马福萨再次当选南非总统几个小时前，他所在的非洲人国民大会与亲商的反对党达成了权力分享协议。其他政党支持现任总统连任五年，作为交换，他将获得内阁职位和立法机构的关键职位。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-18/south-africa-reelects-cyril-ramaphosa-as-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 13:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大保持银行资本水平稳定，称家庭债务风险稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/canada-holds-bank-capital-levels-steady-says-household-debt-risk-is-stable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大金融监管机构维持该国最大银行的资本要求不变，表明官员们认为这些银行的资产负债表足够强劲，能够抵御经济动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/canada-holds-bank-capital-levels-steady-says-household-debt-risk-is-stable</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:52:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
